type: web_research
title: RapidAPI - API Marketplace Quality & Error Handling
source: "https://rapidapi.com/ + best practices guides"
key_insights[6]: Approval workflow for API plans requiring authorization,Management dashboard for usage/cost/error monitoring,Recommendation Engine API with multiple algorithms,Team reviews thousands of APIs for recommendations,Consistent error response structure critical,Standard HTTP status codes as first line of error reporting
findings[4]: API gateway centralizes error management,Retry logic + client-side rate limiting recommended from start,Quality/reliability/documentation vary across marketplace,Specific submission quality standards not publicly detailed
techniques:
  "Error Handling": Consistent JSON structure + HTTP status codes
  Quality: Team review + performance testing
  Monitoring: Dashboard for usage/costs/errors
  Discovery: Recommendation algorithms + manual curation
recommendations[4]: Implement consistent error response format across all taisun_agent APIs,Add centralized error management gateway,Create usage/cost/error monitoring dashboard,Build recommendation engine for skill/agent selection
